  "detailed_description": "<h1>Comparison Grid</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/d6de1f58b5e414b5695b8e6fd2b57927.avif?t=1773761992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras_big/d6de1f58b5e414b5695b8e6fd2b57927.avif?t=1773761992 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Digital Deluxe Edition</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/1550e64b23e29b3367193cbc05828e9c.avif?t=1773761992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras_big/1550e64b23e29b3367193cbc05828e9c.avif?t=1773761992 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Deluxe Edition includes:<br>- The base game<br>- A captain outfit: the Libertine set<br>- The Born With It and Stay Alive emotes<br>- The Pissed and Sea of Tears fireworks<br><br>Persistent internet connection, Ubisoft Account, Microsoft Account, and Game Pass Ultimate or Core (subscriptions sold separately) required.</p></p><br><h1>Premium Edition</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/45d1b44a50438f14838c8c0b7566f80d.avif?t=1773761992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras_big/45d1b44a50438f14838c8c0b7566f80d.avif?t=1773761992 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Premium Edition includes:<br>- The base game<br>- All Deluxe Edition content, including a captain outfit, two emotes, and two fireworks<br>- The Grand Game Collection, including a captain outfit, a ship set, a figurehead, and a firework<br>- The Jack's Noggin pet<br>- The Silver Haze ship aura<br>- Digital art book and selected game soundtrack*<br><br>*Access the digital art book and soundtrack from the official Skull and Bones website: </p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engage in True Naval Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fast, tactical, and explosive ship-to-ship battles built around positioning, timing, and powerful weapon loadouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/2bb4719ef3db7298922ee37fc41c8cb8.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/2bb4719ef3db7298922ee37fc41c8cb8.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/2bb4719ef3db7298922ee37fc41c8cb8.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Fleet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command a variety of unique ship classes – each with distinct roles, perks, and strengths. Customize your vessel to reflect your strategy and playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/b447a6978a5241b01d4fad7d97b3b4a9.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/b447a6978a5241b01d4fad7d97b3b4a9.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/b447a6978a5241b01d4fad7d97b3b4a9.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-op with Friends and Share World Adventures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with fellow captains to form a fleet of up to 20 players to take on challenging world events, fortified settlements, and pirate hunters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a300abf2a17f5bc4a2e5aa93b3cecc6f.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a300abf2a17f5bc4a2e5aa93b3cecc6f.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a300abf2a17f5bc4a2e5aa93b3cecc6f.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy Ever-Evolving Content and Seasonal Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face new threats and mythical encounters as the world continuously expands with regular content updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a459eefacc715f67956cc4927f175c0a.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a459eefacc715f67956cc4927f175c0a.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a459eefacc715f67956cc4927f175c0a.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sail a Living, Immersive Sea</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through a richly realized Indian Ocean with dynamic weather, turbulent waters, hostile factions, roaming threats, and opportunities for high-risk, high-reward encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/3de9a4eef886dfdf057c47788ca011f7.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/3de9a4eef886dfdf057c47788ca011f7.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/3de9a4eef886dfdf057c47788ca011f7.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Persistent internet connection, Ubisoft Account, Microsoft Account, and Game Pass Ultimate or Core (subscriptions sold separately) required.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engage in True Naval Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fast, tactical, and explosive ship-to-ship battles built around positioning, timing, and powerful weapon loadouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/2bb4719ef3db7298922ee37fc41c8cb8.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/2bb4719ef3db7298922ee37fc41c8cb8.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/2bb4719ef3db7298922ee37fc41c8cb8.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Fleet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command a variety of unique ship classes – each with distinct roles, perks, and strengths. Customize your vessel to reflect your strategy and playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/b447a6978a5241b01d4fad7d97b3b4a9.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/b447a6978a5241b01d4fad7d97b3b4a9.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/b447a6978a5241b01d4fad7d97b3b4a9.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-op with Friends and Share World Adventures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with fellow captains to form a fleet of up to 20 players to take on challenging world events, fortified settlements, and pirate hunters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a300abf2a17f5bc4a2e5aa93b3cecc6f.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a300abf2a17f5bc4a2e5aa93b3cecc6f.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a300abf2a17f5bc4a2e5aa93b3cecc6f.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy Ever-Evolving Content and Seasonal Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face new threats and mythical encounters as the world continuously expands with regular content updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a459eefacc715f67956cc4927f175c0a.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a459eefacc715f67956cc4927f175c0a.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/a459eefacc715f67956cc4927f175c0a.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sail a Living, Immersive Sea</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through a richly realized Indian Ocean with dynamic weather, turbulent waters, hostile factions, roaming threats, and opportunities for high-risk, high-reward encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/3de9a4eef886dfdf057c47788ca011f7.poster.avif?t=1773761992\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/3de9a4eef886dfdf057c47788ca011f7.webm?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/3de9a4eef886dfdf057c47788ca011f7.mp4?t=1773761992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Persistent internet connection, Ubisoft Account, Microsoft Account, and Game Pass Ultimate or Core (subscriptions sold separately) required.</p>",
